JAKARTA , Jan. 2 ( Xinhua ) 
JAKARTA , Indonesia 2007-01-02 02:09:29 UTC 
The wreckage of the ill-fated plane was found early Tuesday . 
The Adam Air Boeing 737-400 crashed Monday afternoon , but search and rescue teams only discovered the wreckage early Tuesday . 
A Boeing 737-400 plane with 102 people on board crashed into a mountain in Indonesia 's West Sulawesi province on Monday , killing at least 90 people .
Navy rear commander Eddy Suyanto told el-Shinta radio station that the plane had crashed in a mountainous region in Polewali , west Sulawesi province . 